聘部、销售服务运营部和智能驾驶部门等。具体而言，销售服务运营部门优化超过 400 人，招聘部会从原来的 200 多人缩减至 40-50 人，智驾团队会缩减至 1000 人以内。 知情人士称，4 月底，管理层通过了最终的裁员名单，这轮裁员优化正式启动于 5 月第一周，大部分会在 5 月底前结束，对优化员工实行 N+1 赔偿。理想汽车希望在 6 月 15 日员工股票解禁之前完成大部分的人员优化计划，这样一来可以节省一部分为员工进行股票兑现的成本。 今年 4 月，网上传出有理想汽车员工透露公司的状态，理想汽车则表示网传裁员及预算大幅缩减均不属实。消息称理想汽车开启人员优化，比例超 18%"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-5b104daeadeb3d679240ddce1eaac027_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "70 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/656200976"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I1ty8sof8hJVNEAMaCTEwODEwMDMzNCDBhZeyBjAAODFAEXIJNjU2MjAwOTc2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1716265318.772330", "card_id": "Q_656434031", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "情绪控制能力差的人在现实中有什么方法能避免自己情绪失控？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b268509ad1638e7217504f8043421f86_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/656434031"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I1ty8sof8hJVNEAMaCTEwODE1MTk5MSD22KKyBjAAOCFAEnIJNjU2NDM0MDMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1716265318.773391", "card_id": "Q_656206322", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 25}, "target": {"title_a